<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="33" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="6" pageNumber="33">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="6" pageNumber="33">
The relationships of 
<taxonomicName class="Gastropoda" family="Hydrobiidae" genus="Pyrgulopsis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pyrgulopsis licina" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="6" pageNumber="33" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="licina">Pyrgulopsis licina</taxonomicName>
were not well resolved in the molecular phylogenetic analysis (Fig. 1). Haplotype variation within this clade was relatively small (Appendix II).
</paragraph>
